            },
            {
              "id": "FF1053",
              "name": "buffer/getenv",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "Environment variables are untrustable input if they can be set by an attacker. They can have any content and length, and the same variable can be set more than once (CWE-807, CWE-20)."
